class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-992497c2-451a-492d-b241-9ca296b0bd2c\">이름이 경옥&#x27;고&#x27;잖아요! </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c5dbe1e2-fb8c-4acb-980c-904ab40f1f0b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7e2d8308-a128-45b4-818e-9e07e227daec\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4397e605-f25c-4e3c-8267-035fee24fae7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4397e605-f25c-4e3c-8267-035fee24fae7\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTBfNzIg/MDAxNjczMzMwMDExNDk5.XRLamHxD5TPWY7TmZvht6zJtfLQpI7X-kaHfCP2aSBsg.9uSlgxwE3jhuCkihiBXDsSouU_vLsSH-SPWns0msnAYg.JPEG.isuhani/20180124_121717.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"4032\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTBfNzIg/MDAxNjczMzMwMDExNDk5.XRLamHxD5TPWY7TmZvht6zJtfLQpI7X-kaHfCP2aSBsg.9uSlgxwE3jhuCkihiBXDsSouU_vLsSH-SPWns0msnAYg.JPEG.isuhani/20180124_121717.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTBfNzIg/MDAxNjczMzMwMDExNDk5.XRLamHxD5TPWY7TmZvht6zJtfLQpI7X-kaHfCP2aSBsg.9uSlgxwE3jhuCkihiBXDsSouU_vLsSH-SPWns0msnAYg.JPEG.isuhani/20180124_121717.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"666\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b87176e1-093e-4076-a842-99b767282514\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0e6f9e9d-99d7-4c78-a62c-378521ea0c7c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2fcf7bb2-d643-4f8b-bf28-42ed91f2a48f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6ebe2272-d657-4e8e-87b5-b0905b3b0e6d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-16bb9a19-f33c-4b5d-940a-04ad4a33154a\">그래서 조제방법 그대로 조제를 하면 위의 사진처럼 &#x27;고&#x27; 형태로 만들어지게 되요. 거친형태의 누텔라 라고 표현할 수 있을까요? ^^</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d27d36c1-6fac-48bb-9477-6ff1b4826ba3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b87e79fe-54c7-4811-bbc8-1ccfe9a79ef0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-baa36867-065b-4872-995c-5827db7f2c7c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aa41f291-c3b9-4a24-80e5-7572b372cba8\">&#x27;고&#x27;형태는 위 사진처럼 용기에 담겨져 있는 것을 수저 등을 이용해서 일정량을 덜어서 복용하게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-49f291a5-6391-4389-a396-d6acbc2fca62\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9b2d9f61-873a-4f52-9da8-3dce381d0522\">용기를 열고, 수저로 떠서 복용 하고 다시 용기를 닫는 과정이 바쁜 현대사회에서는 불편할 수 있어서 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1cf2f8ec-c32a-4d2e-91fa-185093050945\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5ac7a492-fdf9-4b1a-be8d-bc3ffddc2d60\">한 번 복용할 분량을 주머니에 혹은 가방에 간편하게 가지고 다니다가 쉽게 짜서 먹을 수 있도록 제형개발을 한 것이 &#x27;경옥고 스틱&#x27; 입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cff53e80-a752-426e-8a34-ab81fb9afaa5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-29003b69-23af-4d78-aab6-46f02a0f0aab\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-05f2b9f1-e116-4130-b320-ab2b0c6671fd\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-05f2b9f1-e116-4130-b320-ab2b0c6671fd\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTBfMTM0/MDAxNjczMzI5OTg2NzQ2.KkQHGFQXPjzXFvArh2P7pQbrqj1cvHVGowlyXOvq2bQg.yXmh95pWjgRoJEnx3IJKWrU3Qoosof54UivcAaVNO5Ug.JPEG.isuhani/%EA%B2%BD%EC%98%A5%EA%B3%A0_%EC%8A%A4%ED%8B%B1_%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%84.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1165\", \"originalHeight\" : \"903\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzAxMTBfMTM0/MDAxNjczMzI5OTg2NzQ2.KkQHGFQXPjzXFvArh2P7pQbrqj1cvHVGowlyXOvq2bQg.yXmh95pWjgRoJEnx3IJKWrU3Qoosof54UivcAaVNO5Ug.JPEG.isuhani/%EA%B2%BD%EC%98%A5%EA%B3%A0_%EC%8A%A4%ED%8B%B1_%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%84.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-